20 'PART C
21 Sec. C-1. 30-A MRSA §4722, sub-§1, ¶DD, as amended by PL 2021, c. 671, §1,
22 is further amended by amending subparagraph (1), division (b) to read:
23 (b) "Affordable housing project" means a multifamily rental housing project
24 that contains at least 5 units of affordable housing and in which:
25 (i) At least 50% of the aggregate square feet of the completed project is
26 housing of which at least 50% of the aggregate square feet of the
27 completed housing creates new affordable housing; or
28 (ii) At least 33% of the aggregate square feet of the completed project
29 creates new affordable housing.
30 Sec. C-2. 36 MRSA §5219-BB, sub-§1, ¶A, as amended by PL 2009, c. 361, §28
31 and affected by §37, is further amended to read:
32 A. "Certified affordable housing project" means a decent, safe and sanitary dwelling,
33 apartment or other living accommodation multifamily rental housing project that
