18 SUMMARY
1199 This amendment eliminates the bill's revisions to the caps on the rehabilitation credits
2200 for historic properties and affordable housing. The amendment also relieves the Maine
2211 State Housing Authority of the obligation to certify for the credit affordable housing
2222 projects with fewer than 5 units.
